(Upon termination of employment or transfer to another department,) Tj
T* (employees are required to undergo an exit process for the proper) Tj
T* (handover of company assets. Employees must return all assigned) Tj
T* (assets to the IT department for review and assessment. The IT team will) Tj
T* (conduct a thorough inspection of the returned assets to identify any) Tj
T* (damages, missing items, or non-functional components. A report) Tj
T* (detailing the condition of the assets will be submitted to the HR) Tj
T* (department for record-keeping and further action. Based on the IT) Tj
T* (team's report, the HR department will initiate the recovery process for) Tj
T* (damaged, missing, or non-functional assets. Recovery of costs) Tj
T* (associated with damaged, missing, or non-functional assets will be) Tj
T* (handled on a case-by-case basis and may be deducted from the) Tj
T* (employee's Full and Final settlement \(F&F\) if necessary.) Tj
