(In the event of theft, the recovery amount will be determined based on) Tj
T* (the asset's current market value and its age. The depreciation of the) Tj
T* (asset will also be taken into account, and the recovery amount will be) Tj
T* (deducted from the employee's salary or any pending dues, subject to) Tj
T* (the company's recovery process. For damages to assets, the cost of) Tj
T* (replacement parts and repair services will be calculated based on the) Tj
T* (age of the asset and the prevailing market rates. If the damage is severe) Tj
T* (or irreparable, the entire cost of asset replacement or repair will be) Tj
T* (recovered from the employee. In cases where damages are caused) Tj
T* (intentionally or due to negligence, the entire cost of asset replacement) Tj
T* (or repair, including spares and labor, will be recovered from the) Tj
T* (employee.) Tj
